Code preview of the table MD_合同信息接口表

drop table "MD_Contract" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "MD_Contract" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "MD_Contract"
(
"ContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"SAPContractCode" VARCHAR2(20),
BCID NUMBER(32),
"BoothType" INTEGER,
"CompanyID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"CompanyName" NVARCHAR2(50) not null,
"EntityID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"EntityName" NVARCHAR2(50),
"MallID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"MallCode" VARCHAR2(30) not null,
"BuildingID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"BuildingCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"OperateType" INTEGER not null,
"ContractTypeID" INTEGER not null,
"ContractTypeCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"ContractStartDate" TIMESTAMP not null,
"ContractEndDate" TIMESTAMP not null,
"ContractActualEndDate" TIMESTAMP,
"ContractDayNum" INTEGER not null,
"ContractActualDayNum" INTEGER,
"UnitPrice" NUMBER(10,2) not null,
"BudgetaryPrice" DECIMAL(20, 2),
"TotalArea" NUMBER(10,2) not null,
"TotaIIncome" NUMBER(10,2) not null,
"DiscountTotalAmount" NUMBER(10,2),
"ContractStatusCode" INTEGER not null,
"SourceFrom" INTEGER not null,
"OrderDate" TIMESTAMP,
"RenewContractCode" VARCHAR(20),
"IsEffect" INTEGER,
"EffectTime" TIMESTAMP,
"IsCancel" INTEGER,
"CancelTime" TIMESTAMP,
"IsTermination" INTEGER,
"ActualTerminationTime" TIMESTAMP,
"IsStopCurrentMap" INTEGER,
"StopCurrentMapTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ReceiveTime" TIMESTAMP,
"AntiActivationTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_MD_CONTRACT primary key ("ContractID")
);

comment on table "MD_Contract" is
'招商可视化接收合同时间：在异动方案和合同流程图中的第7步下发费用单之前（财务审核通过之后）

合同信息接口表：';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."BoothType" is
'8:标准展位，7:非标准展位，6：广告位
';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."OperateType" is
'经营类型是指商场签订合同时的类型，跟商场经营类型无关
1：自营 2:委管
';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."ContractTypeID" is
'1:展位租赁合同 2:广告位协议';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."ContractTypeCode" is
'Z001 自营招商租赁合同
Z002 委管招商租赁合同
Z020 固定广告资源协议
Z030 其他广告资源协议';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."ContractStatusCode" is
'10: 创建草稿
20: 提交到SAP
30; 待财务复核
40; 待商总审核
50; 待财务激活
60; 已激活
70; 已过账
71：已终止

31: 财务复核时退回（未复核）
41: 商总审核时退回（未审核）
51: 财务激活时退回（未激活）
61: 反激活 （财务反激活退回）

21：退回后并修改 （包括反激活）

80：已取消

90：商总审核通过（临时合同）
';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."SourceFrom" is
'1:来自异动方案 2:来自续签 3:来自更正重签
';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."IsEffect" is
'1:已处理
0：未处理';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."IsCancel" is
'根据生效时间更新当前经营图时使用
合同取消（仅限于招商可视化）：合同结束时间小于合同生效时间';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."IsTermination" is
'0:正常
1：终止';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."ActualTerminationTime" is
'租赁合同终止时填写的合同实际结束时间应满足：填写时的当前时间—填写的合同实际结束时间<30天';

comment on column "MD_Contract"."ReceiveTime" is
'招商可视化接收合同时间：在异动方案和合同流程图中的第7步下发费用单之前（财务审核通过之后）';
